  m_Name: 4_BirdWatch
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Game.Collectable.CollectableItem
  id: 4_BirdWatch
  headerName: BIRD WATCHING
  content: "(A frantic scribble on the back of a grocery list)\r\n\r\nThe birds aren't
    flying. I walked up the ridge to check on the nest, and the three of them are
    just... sitting in the dirt. They didn't even flinch when I got close. They\u2019re
    staring into the treeline.\r\n\r\nActually, they aren't staring. Their heads
    are tilted, like they\u2019re listening to the roots. I tried to make a noise
    to scare them off\u2014a clap, a shout\u2014but my voice felt heavy. Like the
    air is getting thicker, like it\u2019s turning into sap. It\u2019s still a beautiful
    day. The sun is gold. So why am I shivering?"
  type: 0
  icon: {fileID: 0}
  dialogData: {fileID: 0}
